high_descs: Stand in front of the microwave
Open the microwave and take the plastic container out
Close the microwave and walk to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator and put the plastic tub inside and close the refrigerator, open the refrigerator again, take out the plastic container, and close the refrigerator again.
Walk to the microwave and open it.
Put the plastic container inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Take the plastic container from the microwave, cool it in the refrigerator, put it back in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk forward across the room and turn to face the microwave on the right.
Get the dish out of the microwave.
Turn to the right and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the dish inside the refrigerator and close the door. Open the door and remove the dish.
Turn to the left and walk to the microwave.
Put the dish inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Exchange the dish in the microwave for the one from the refrigerator.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn right to face the microwave.
Take the bowl out of the microwave.
Move to the right and go to the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge.
Return to the microwave on your left.
Put the bowl in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk forward to face the microwave.
Take the bowl out of the microwave.
Step to the right to face the fridge.
Cool the bowl in the fridge and then pick it back up.
Take a step to the left to face the microwave.
Place the bowl in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To heat a bowl and put it back in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk to the microwave on the right.
Open the microwave and pick up the clear container.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the container in the fridge, wait a few seconds, and take it back out.
Turn left and walk back to the microwave.
Heat the container in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled container in the microwave.

open microwave door, pick up glass dish from inside microwave, close the door
walk right to face the fridge
open fridge door, place dish on second shelf from the top, close the door, wait for dish to be chilled, open fridge door, pick up dish from inside fridge, close the door

open microwave door, place glass dish inside microwave, close the door
